g.text: For TPS55165-Q1, Connect TP_FB to TP_VREG for 12V output and to GND for 5V output. DNP Rfbb and Rfbt.
When PG_Delay is 0.7ms, Connect TP_DELAY to GND.
When PG_Delay is 40ms, Connect TP_DELAY to TP_VREG.
For PFM Mode, Connect TP_MODE to VIN
For PWM Mode, Connect TP_MODE to GND
When IGN PWRL is Disabled, Connect TP_IGN to GND.
